      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――里帰りライブ当日inシーパラ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Homecoming live day at Sea Paradise",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.6066667795000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 2.0666667223
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 3.8000001033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "星見市のみんな～、久しぶり～！\n私達の里帰りライブに来てくれてありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in Hoshimi City~‚ long time no see~!\nThank you for coming to our homecoming live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8000001033,
      "endTime": 13.306711872400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.5000001033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんの応援のおかげで、私達はBIG4になって\nこの街に凱旋することが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to everyone's support‚ we became BIG4 and\nwere able to return triumphantly to this city.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5000001033,
      "endTime": 20.3779817661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.5907944124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "応援してくれたみんなの声、ちゃんと届いてるよ\nだから今日は、私達がみんなにお返しをする番！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's cheering voices are reaching us properly.\nSo today‚ it's our turn to return the favor to everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5907944124,
      "endTime": 29.404445306600003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.5907944124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "感謝の想いを込めた今日のステージ\n最後まで楽しんで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's stage is filled with our gratitude.\nPlease enjoy it until the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5907944124,
      "endTime": 34.2888218325,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4175.872254299996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 34.5016337157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（最初から凄い盛り上がりだな。それだけ星見市の）\n（ファンが今日のライブを待ち望んでいたということか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What an amazing energy from the start. That's how much）\n（the fans in Hoshimi City were looking forward to today's live.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5016337157,
      "endTime": 42.5221551657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.734967049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらもいつにも増して張り切っているが……）\n（これは本番前にあったサプライズの効果かな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura is more enthusiastic than usual too…）\n（I wonder if this is the effect of the surprise before the show?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.734967049,
      "endTime": 49.638889893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブが始まる少し前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A little before the live starts",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5349639972,
      "endTime": 51.8816289505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 51.8816289505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本番前の最後のリハーサルも終わって\n後は開演を待つだけだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The final rehearsal before the show is over\nand now we just wait for the opening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7349634887,
      "endTime": 57.8594306709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 58.068296822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "リハーサルはいい感じでしたね\n新曲の振り付けもばっちり決まってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rehearsal went well.\nThe choreography for the new song was also perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.068296822,
      "endTime": 64.0109517178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 64.2016321899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "新衣装も凄く可愛くて\nお客さんの反応が今から楽しみだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The new costumes are really cute too.\nI'm looking forward to the audience's reaction.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2016321899,
      "endTime": 69.95049855719999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 70.1349655232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "コラボ企画も沢山準備したし\nシーパラコラボを楽しんでもらえているといいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've prepared lots of collaboration projects‚\nso I hope everyone enjoys the Sea Paradise collaboration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1349655232,
      "endTime": 76.38700619560001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 76.5998180789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。……ところで、本番前に\nみんなに話しておきたいことがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. …By the way‚ before the show\nthere's something I want to tell everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5998180789,
      "endTime": 82.37836660570001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 82.5664847455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "実は……みんなが星見市で里帰りライブをすると聞いて\nある大物ゲストが極秘で会いに来てくれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… when they heard you were doing a homecoming live in Hoshimi City‚\na big-name guest secretly came to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5664847455,
      "endTime": 90.4758044324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4016357502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "大物ゲスト？　一体誰ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A big-name guest? Who could it be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6664847455,
      "endTime": 95.0532877049,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10168.0970429
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2660995883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "紹介しよう。サプライズで急遽駆けつけてくれたのは\n……この方だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me introduce them. The one who rushed here as a surprise is\n…this individual!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2660995883,
      "endTime": 101.6886166972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "ギョんにちは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyood afternoon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.199428344,
      "endTime": 104.54945106529999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 104.7622629486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "わあああああああ！　魚魚っとさんだー！！\nかっこいいー！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaaaah! It's Gyogyo-tto-san!!\nSo cool!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7622629486,
      "endTime": 111.3312200867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 111.5289296153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "かっこいい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cool…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5289296153,
      "endTime": 113.4587306502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 113.6715425335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-gyogyo002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらギョンがわしのファンだと聞いて\n星見漁港から駆けつけたギョ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that Sakura-gyo is my fan\nso I rushed here from Hoshimi Port‚ gyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6715425335,
      "endTime": 119.9372341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1500459834
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-gyogyo003.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースと月のテンペストのみんな\n今日はよろしくだギョ！　GYOGYO～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone from Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest\nplease take care of me today‚ gyo! GYOGYO~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1500459834,
      "endTime": 127.569615285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7824271683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさんが私に会いに……！\n嬉しい！　これって夢じゃないよね？",
      "translations": {
