      "text": "直前に思いついて急いで用意したサプライズ\nプレゼントもなんとか間に合って良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The surprise present we thought of at the last minute and hurriedly prepared\nsomehow made it in time‚ which was good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.5616230854,
      "endTime": 290.4976776012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 290.6949564187
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、今日来てくれたみんなが\n帰り道にあれを見て、笑顔になってくれたらいいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ I hope everyone who came today\nwill see that on their way home and smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.6949564187,
      "endTime": 298.2828478066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 298.49565969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "……ライブ、楽しんでもらえたかな？\n感謝の気持ちは、ちゃんと届いたかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder if everyone enjoyed the live?\nWould our feelings of gratitude properly reach them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.49565969,
      "endTime": 308.7165667105,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11775.869281799998
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16071.009519799987
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 308.9289930233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと届いてるわ\nだってほら、会場の拍手が全然鳴り止まないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They properly reached them.\nLook‚ the applause from the venue isn't stopping at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.9289930233,
      "endTime": 315.95414027059996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 316.1669521539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "……本当だ\nみんなの拍手の音がここまで聞こえてくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right.\nI can hear everyone's applause all the way here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.1669521539,
      "endTime": 325.24772340939995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 325.4336188206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "地元っていいわね。今日のイベントで私達にとって\n星見市は特別なんだって改めて思ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hometown is nice. Through today's event‚ I realized once again\nthat Hoshimi City is special to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.4336188206,
      "endTime": 335.8842993627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 336.0971112459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "この街のみんなの想いに応えられるように\nこれからもアイドルとして輝いていかないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we can respond to everyone's feelings in this city\nwe have to keep shining as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.0971112459,
      "endTime": 343.726884672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 343.9304445793
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……今日のライブ、本当に楽しかった\n忘れられない思い出がまた一つ増えたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Today's live was really fun.\nAnother unforgettable memory has been added.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.9304445793,
      "endTime": 353.047973304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 353.2607851873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。ファンのみんなにとっても\n忘れられない日になってたらいいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. I hope it became\nan unforgettable day for all the fans too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.2607851873,
      "endTime": 359.94314326150004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 360.127451854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、琴乃ちゃん\nいつかまた、ここで里帰りライブをやろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kotono-chan.\nLet's do a homecoming live here again someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.127451854,
      "endTime": 367.5423953583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 367.727451854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、いつかまた、この街で、この場所で……\n一緒に、里帰りライブをしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ someday again‚ in this city‚ at this place…\nLet's do a homecoming live together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.727451854,
      "endTime": 377.3223041109,
